03e\n\u003ctable style=\"width: 99.9834%; height: 174.476px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eFORMA:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eRedonda\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eBALANCE:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eMedio Bajo\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eMARCO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eFibra de Vidrio\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eNÚCLEO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eEVA28\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003ePLANO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003eFibra de Vidrio\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003ePESO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 24.4965px;\"\u003e355 gr \/ 375 gr\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 27.4965px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 41.3846%; height: 27.4965px;\"\u003eACABADO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.5517%; height: 27.4965px;\"\u003eBrillo + Sand\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003c\/tbody\u003e\n\u003c\/table\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-metrics\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003ePotencia\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e90\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003eControl\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle control\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e97\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content2\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVairo Across Yellow Sand Finish\u003c\/strong\u003e es tu pala para \u003cstrong\u003einiciarte en el pádel\u003c\/strong\u003e. Este modelo se ha diseñado para \u003cstrong\u003ejugadores principiantes\u003c\/strong\u003e que empiezan con su toma de contacto con el pádel. Es una pala de \u003cstrong\u003ecuerpo redondo\u003c\/strong\u003e cuyo peso ronda los \u003cstrong\u003e360 gramos\u003c\/strong\u003e. Se siente \u003cstrong\u003efácil de manejar\u003c\/strong\u003e y cómoda en cada golpe. Está hecha con \u003cstrong\u003emateriales elásticos\u003c\/strong\u003e y \u003cstrong\u003etecnologías que te dan las mejores sensaciones\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePara empezar en el pádel hay que elegir una \u003cstrong\u003ebuena pala\u003c\/strong\u003e. Este modelo está diseñado para cubrir \u003cstrong\u003etodas las necesidades en pista\u003c\/strong\u003e de los jugadores nuevos. Se te hará \u003cstrong\u003esúper fácil aprender a manejar la pala\u003c\/strong\u003e y a \u003cstrong\u003econtrolar los golpes\u003c\/strong\u003e. Tiene un \u003cstrong\u003ebalance bajo\u003c\/strong\u003e y un \u003cstrong\u003etacto medio-blando\u003c\/strong\u003e, una pala perfecta para \u003cstrong\u003easentar las bases de este deporte\u003c\/strong\u003e.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content3\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eUNDERGRIP ABSORPTION:\u003c\/strong\u003e La malla de “Expandex PC16”, ubicada entre la base del puño de la pala y el grip, hace posible sentir una mayor suavidad y confort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSPOT ZONE:\u003c\/strong\u003e Utilizamos el sistema desarrollado por Vairo Spin technology, que es la unión de las láminas de fibra más elásticas con abrasivo aplicadas en la cara externa del núcleo de la pala.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eABSORPTION SHOCK:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sistema antivibratorio dual, externo de la paleta, que es utilizado por Vairo en exclusiva. Reduce considerablemente las vibraciones que se producen en el momento del golpe.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eABSORVENT GRIP:\u003c\/strong\u003e La alta capacidad de absorción del grip se debe a la mezcla de gomas blandas que evita que la pala resbale. Es perfecto para jugadores que necesiten un grip absorbente con buen agarre.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","published_at":"2026-05-04T16:21:30-03:00","created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo","product_type":"","tags":["Across Yellow Sand Finish","Formato Redondo","Palas de Padel Vairo - Argentina \u003e Advanced Eva Series \u003e Sand Finish"],"variants":[{"id":48268918259917,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"608001126 0101","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":{"id":54215389053133,"product_id":9032067940557,"position":1,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","updated_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","alt":null,"width":1080,"height":1080,"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/ACROSS-YELLOW-SAND-FINISH-FRENTE-NUEVA.jpg?v=1751543992","variant_ids":[48268918259917]},"available":true,"price":"222000.00","grams":400,"compare_at_price":"0.00","position":1,"product_id":9032067940557,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:53-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54215389053133,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","product_id":9032067940557,"variant_ids":[48268918259917],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/ACROSS-YELLOW-SAND-FINISH-FRENTE-NUEVA.jpg?v=1751543992","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215389085901,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","product_id":9032067940557,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/ACROSS-YELLOW-SAND-FINISH-LADO1.jpg?v=1751543992","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215389118669,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","position":3,"updated_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","product_id":9032067940557,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/ACROSS-YELLOW-SAND-FINISH-LADO2.jpg?v=1751543992","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215389151437,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","position":4,"updated_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:52-03:00","product_id":9032067940557,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/ACROSS-YELLOW-SAND-FINISH-PERFIL.jpg?v=1751543992","width":1080,"height":1080}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":9032067645645,"title":"Black Karbon Confort","handle":"black-karbon-confort","body_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIncluye: \u003c\/strong\u003eFunda con cierre\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJuega con un magnífico control gracias a la Vairo Black Karbon Confort, una pala híbrida para jugadores avanzados. Con la tecnología Power Bridge.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight-box\"\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNivel de Juego:\u003c\/strong\u003e Avanzado \/ Competición   |   \u003cstrong\u003eTipo de Juego:\u003c\/strong\u003e Control + Potencia\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"tabs-minimal\"\u003e\n\u003cinput type=\"radio\" name=\"tabs\" id=\"tab1\" checked\u003e \u003cinput type=\"radio\" name=\"tabs\" id=\"tab2\"\u003e \u003cinput type=\"radio\" name=\"tabs\" id=\"tab3\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"tab-labels\"\u003e\n\u003clabel for=\"tab1\"\u003eCARACTERÍSTICAS\u003c\/label\u003e \u003clabel for=\"tab2\"\u003eDESCRIPCIÓN\u003c\/label\u003e \u003clabel for=\"tab3\"\u003eTECNOLOGÍA\u003c\/label\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"tab-content\"\u003e\n\u003c!-- CARACTERÍSTICAS --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content1\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"caracteristicas-grid\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eFORMA:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eHíbrida\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eBALANCE:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eMedio Alto\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eMARCO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eCarbono\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eNÚCLEO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eEVA28\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003ePLANO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e18k Textreme\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003ePESO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003e365 gr \/ 375 gr\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eACABADO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eMate + Sand Finis\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003c\/tbody\u003e\n\u003c\/table\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-metrics\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003ePotencia\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e95\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003eControl\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle control\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e95\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!-- DESCRIPCIÓN --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content2\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLa \u003cstrong\u003eVairo Black Karbon Confort\u003c\/strong\u003e es una pala pensada para jugadores exigentes de nivel avanzado que opten por un juego más de control y disfruten golpeando la bola con efecto. Es \u003cstrong\u003efácil de manejar\u003c\/strong\u003e gracias a su peso de entre 365 y 375 gramos.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCon un \u003cstrong\u003eformato híbrido y un balance intermedio\u003c\/strong\u003e, esta pala \u003cstrong\u003eVairo\u003c\/strong\u003e tiene un punto dulce amplio que permite golpear con \u003cstrong\u003eprecisión, control y estabilidad\u003c\/strong\u003e. Al mismo tiempo se genera velocidad y potencia en cada golpe para poder sorprender al oponente.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!-- TECNOLOGÍA --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content3\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eREINFORCED ZONE:\u003c\/strong\u003e Doble estructura de carbono en los laterales del corazón de la pala: minimiza las torsiones y vibraciones producidas con el impacto de la bola.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSPEED SHOT:\u003c\/strong\u003e Arquitectura interna triangular que genera un corazón rígido y un sweet spot un 20% mayor.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eCARBON COMPOSITE:\u003c\/strong\u003e Material rígido y ligero que mejora control y rendimiento.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eDUAL INTEGRATED COLUMNS:\u003c\/strong\u003e Tubos de carbono en el corazón que aumentan la estabilidad y dominio de la pala.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eUNDERGRIP ABSORPTION:\u003c\/strong\u003e Malla “Expandex PC16” que aporta mayor confort en el grip.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSPOT ZONE:\u003c\/strong\u003e Láminas de fibra con abrasivo aplicadas para mejorar el efecto y la superficie de contacto.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eABSORPTION SHOCK:\u003c\/strong\u003e Sistema antivibratorio exclusivo de Vairo que reduce notablemente las vibraciones.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eABSORVENT GRIP:\u003c\/strong\u003e Gomas blandas que evitan que la pala resbale, ofreciendo gran absorción y agarre.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","published_at":"2026-05-04T16:24:45-03:00","created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:17-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo","product_type":"Palas","tags":["Black Karbon Confort","Formato Híbrido","Palas de Padel Vairo - Argentina \u003e Professional Premium"],"variants":[{"id":48268917965005,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"608001138 0101","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":false,"price":"399000.00","grams":400,"compare_at_price":"0.00","position":1,"product_id":9032067645645,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:18-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54956592234701,"created_at":"2026-04-15T16:48:12-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-04-15T16:48:30-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BLACKKARBONCONFORT.png?v=1776282510","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215385481421,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:18-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2026-04-15T16:48:30-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BLACK-KARBON-CONFORT-LADO1.jpg?v=1776282510","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215385514189,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:18-03:00","position":3,"updated_at":"2026-04-15T16:48:30-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BLACK-KARBON-CONFORT-LADO2.jpg?v=1776282510","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215385546957,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:59:18-03:00","position":4,"updated_at":"2026-04-15T16:48:30-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BLACK-KARBON-CONFORT-PERFIL.jpg?v=1776282510","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":55021586415821,"created_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:31-03:00","position":5,"updated_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:32-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BKCONFORT10.jpg?v=1779304772","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":55021586448589,"created_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:31-03:00","position":6,"updated_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:32-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BKCONFORT13.jpg?v=1779304772","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":55021586481357,"created_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:31-03:00","position":7,"updated_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:32-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BKCONFORT12.jpg?v=1779304772","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":55021586514125,"created_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:31-03:00","position":8,"updated_at":"2026-05-20T16:19:32-03:00","product_id":9032067645645,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/BKCONFORT11.jpg?v=1779304772","width":1080,"height":1080}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":9032067580109,"title":"Black Karbon Speed","handle":"black-karbon-speed","body_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIncluye\u003c\/strong\u003e: funda con cierre\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDestaca con un juego polivalente y versátil gracias a la Vairo Black Karbon Speed, pala híbrida con núcleo de goma EVA. Reforzada con Power Bridge.\u003c\/str