"updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"},{"id":48359216873677,"title":"XL","option1":"XL","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"228001012 0501","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"75000.00","grams":500,"compare_at_price":"0.00","position":5,"product_id":9045387411661,"created_at":"2025-08-05T17:18:13-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"},{"id":48359216906445,"title":"2XL","option1":"2XL","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"228001012 0601","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"75000.00","grams":500,"compare_at_price":"0.00","position":6,"product_id":9045387411661,"created_at":"2025-08-05T17:18:13-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54377422389453,"created_at":"2025-08-05T17:19:55-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2025-08-05T17:19:57-03:00","product_id":9045387411661,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/Joggerlightmoove-espaldanegro_ce0c2a5b-8400-4190-b5ec-1773c6607619.jpg?v=1754425197","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54377422422221,"created_at":"2025-08-05T17:19:55-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2025-08-05T17:19:57-03:00","product_id":9045387411661,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/Joggerlightmoove-frentenegro_83c6d76b-627f-4d23-b1be-d78fe6dc7b77.jpg?v=1754425197","width":1080,"height":1080}],"options":[{"name":"Talla","position":1,"values":["XS","S","M","L","XL","2XL"]}]},{"id":9100204867789,"title":"Kit Avanzado","handle":"kit-avanzado-1","body_html":"\u003cp data-start=\"33\" data-end=\"264\"\u003ePensado para jugadores exigentes que buscan el máximo rendimiento en cada punto. El Kit Avanzado Vairo reúne tecnología, potencia controlada y protección en una combinación que representa la esencia de la marca dentro de la cancha.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"266\" data-end=\"654\"\u003eIncluye la icónica \u003cstrong data-start=\"285\" data-end=\"316\"\u003ePala Vairo Grapheno Confort\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan data-start=\"285\" data-end=\"316\"\u003e 9.1\u003c\/span\u003e desarrollada con tecnología en carbono para ofrecer una sensación superior, excelente salida de bola y un equilibrio ideal entre control y potencia; un tubo de \u003cstrong data-start=\"479\" data-end=\"500\"\u003epelotas Vairo Pro\u003c\/strong\u003e, reconocidas por su rebote consistente y gran durabilidad; y un \u003cstrong data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"584\"\u003eClear Protector\u003c\/strong\u003e, que protege el marco de la pala sin alterar su diseño.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"656\" data-end=\"782\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003eUn kit de alto nivel, ideal para jugadores avanzados que buscan rendimiento, confiabilidad y la identidad Vairo en cada golpe.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-01-22T15:57:38-03:00","created_at":"2026-01-16T15:33:45-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo Padel","product_type":"","tags":[],"variants":[{"id":48523233689805,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"301001033","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"242250.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":"285000.00","position":1,"product_id":9100204867789,"created_at":"2026-01-16T15:33:45-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54745562579149,"created_at":"2026-01-16T15:37:54-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-01-16T15:39:10-03:00","product_id":9100204867789,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/KITAVANZADO2_085a226f-cfb1-457d-a202-a764bc4ba189.jpg?v=1768588750","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215374995661,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:57:49-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2026-01-16T15:39:10-03:00","product_id":9100204867789,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/tubo-de-pelotas.jpg?v=1768588750","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215367950541,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:56:43-03:00","position":3,"updated_at":"2026-01-16T15:39:10-03:00","product_id":9100204867789,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/GRAPHENO-CONFORT-01.jpg?v=1768588750","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215379583181,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:58:29-03:00","position":4,"updated_at":"2026-01-16T15:39:10-03:00","product_id":9100204867789,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/CLEAR-PROTECTOR.jpg?v=1768588750","width":1080,"height":1080}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":9095667613901,"title":"Kit de inicio","handle":"kit-de-inicio","body_html":"\u003cp data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"244\"\u003eTodo lo que necesitás para empezar a jugar al pádel, en un solo kit. El Kit Inicial Vairo fue pensado para quienes dan sus primeros pasos en la cancha y buscan calidad, confort y protección desde el primer punto.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"246\" data-end=\"567\"\u003eIncluye un tubo de \u003cstrong data-start=\"265\" data-end=\"286\"\u003ePelotas Vairo Pro\u003c\/strong\u003e, diseñadas para ofrecer un rebote constante y una excelente durabilidad; un \u003cstrong data-start=\"363\" data-end=\"388\"\u003eCross One Cushion Grip\u003c\/strong\u003e, que mejora el agarre, absorbe las vibraciones y aporta mayor comodidad en cada golpe; y un \u003cstrong data-start=\"481\" data-end=\"500\"\u003ePower Protector\u003c\/strong\u003e, ideal para proteger el marco de la pala y prolongar su vida útil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"569\" data-end=\"739\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003eUn kit práctico, funcional y confiable, perfecto para entrenamientos, partidos recreativos o como primer equipamiento para iniciarse en el pádel con el respaldo de Vairo.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2025-12-16T12:11:11-03:00","created_at":"2025-12-15T10:28:10-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo Padel","product_type":"","tags":[],"variants":[{"id":48510942838989,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"301001030","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"40375.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":"47500.00","position":1,"product_id":9095667613901,"created_at":"2025-12-15T10:28:10-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54693823119565,"created_at":"2025-12-15T14:40:04-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2025-12-15T14:40:47-03:00","product_id":9095667613901,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/KITINICIO.jpg?v=1765820447","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54693824463053,"created_at":"2025-12-15T14:45:07-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2025-12-15T14:45:19-03:00","product_id":9095667613901,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/CROSSONECUSHIONGRIP.jpg?v=1765820719","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215374995661,"created_at":"2025-07-03T08:57:49-03:00","position":3,"updated_at":"2026-01-16T15:39:10-03:00","product_id":9095667613901,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/tubo-de-pelotas.jpg?v=1768588750","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215407665357,"created_at":"2025-07-03T09:03:01-03:00","position":4,"updated_at":"2025-12-15T14:45:19-03:00","product_id":9095667613901,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/power-protector-verde.png?v=1765820719","width":800,"height":800}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":9095667744973,"title":"Kit intermedio","handle":"kit-intermedio","body_html":"\u003cp data-start=\"35\" data-end=\"273\"\u003eDiseñado para jugadores que ya dieron sus primeros pasos y buscan elevar su nivel de juego. El Kit Intermedio Vairo combina rendimiento, control y confort en una selección pensada para entrenamientos más exigentes y partidos competitivos.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"649\"\u003eIncluye la \u003cstrong data-start=\"286\" data-end=\"311\"\u003ePala Vairo Carbon One\u003c\/strong\u003e, fabricada con carbono para ofrecer mayor precisión, solidez y una excelente respuesta en cada golpe; un tubo de \u003cstrong data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"446\"\u003epelotas Vairo Pro\u003c\/strong\u003e, que garantizan un rebote uniforme y gran durabilidad; y un set de \u003cstrong data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"543\"\u003eOvergrips Confort Tack x3\u003c\/strong\u003e, ideales para mejorar el agarre, absorber la transpiración y mantener el control durante todo el partido.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"785\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003eUn kit equilibrado y confiable, perfecto para quienes buscan consolidar su juego y seguir creciendo en la cancha con la calidad Vairo.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2025-12-16T12:11:12-03:00","created_at":"2025-12-15T10:31:16-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo Padel","product_type":"","tags":[],"variants":[{"id":48510942970061,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"301001031","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":false,"price":"217000.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":"230600.00","position":1,"product_id":9095667744973,"created_at":"2025-12-15T10:31:17-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":54693818695885,"created_at":"2025-12-15T14:32:42-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2025-12-15T14:33:02-03:00","product_id":9095667744973,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/KIT_INTERMEDIOI.jpg?v=1765819982","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54215369359565,