tr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eFORMA:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHybrid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eDIMENSIONES:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e41.5cm x 18.5cm\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eMARCO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTpu Edge Guard\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eNÚCLEO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8mm PP Honeycomb Core\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003ePESO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e225gr 10+\/-\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eACABADO:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eArenado\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr style=\"height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 43.6361%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003eCOLOR:\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003ctd style=\"width: 56.0991%; height: 19.6px;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGris\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/td\u003e\n\u003c\/tr\u003e\n\u003c\/tbody\u003e\n\u003c\/table\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-metrics\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003ePotencia\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e87\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle-label\"\u003eControl\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"circle control\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e92\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 14px;\"\u003e%\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!-- DESCRIPCIÓN --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content2\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-end=\"587\" data-start=\"325\"\u003eLa paleta \u003cstrong data-end=\"344\" data-start=\"335\"\u003eNeuro\u003c\/strong\u003e presenta una forma \u003cstrong data-end=\"374\" data-start=\"364\"\u003eHybrid\u003c\/strong\u003e con medidas de 41.5 x 18.5 cm, ideal para lograr un balance entre control y potencia. Su núcleo brinda una respuesta consistente en cada golpe, mientras que su construcción resistente acompaña el ritmo del juego.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-end=\"848\" data-start=\"589\"\u003eEl marco reforzado protege la paleta del uso diario, y su acabado arenado permite generar mejores efectos. Con un peso de 225 g (+\/-10), resulta cómoda y versátil para distintos estilos de juego. Su diseño en color gris le aporta un estilo moderno y elegante.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!-- TECNOLOGÍA --\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"content3\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHIGH RESPONSIVE CORE:\u003c\/strong\u003e Núcleo de alta respuesta que maximiza la salida de la pelota, brindando mayor potencia, control y una sensación sólida en cada golpe.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"413\" data-start=\"376\"\u003eMayor potencia sin esfuerzo extra\u003c\/strong\u003e: la paleta “despide” mejor la pelota.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"473\" data-start=\"456\"\u003eMejor control\u003c\/strong\u003e: la respuesta es más predecible y uniforme.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"546\" data-start=\"522\"\u003eSensación más sólida\u003c\/strong\u003e: reduce vibraciones y mejora el “feeling” en cada golpe.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-end=\"653\" data-start=\"608\"\u003eOptimización del punto dulce (sweet spot)\u003c\/strong\u003e: más superficie útil para golpear bien.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","published_at":"2026-05-29T08:48:15-03:00","created_at":"2026-04-09T09:10:53-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00","vendor":"Vairo","product_type":"Palas","tags":["Neuro","Palas de Pickleball Vairo - Argentina"],"variants":[{"id":48551137116365,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"608001158  0101","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"142000.00","grams":400,"compare_at_price":"142000.00","position":1,"product_id":9109737537741,"created_at":"2026-04-09T09:10:53-03:00","updated_at":"2026-06-12T15:10:32-03:00"}],"images":[{"id":55043182952653,"created_at":"2026-06-05T08:30:09-03:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-06-05T08:30:10-03:00","product_id":9109737537741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/NEURO01_2a210bad-c9bc-4e3c-9228-1cc317a263d9.jpg?v=1780659010","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54937146589389,"created_at":"2026-04-09T09:21:30-03:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2026-04-16T14:15:14-03:00","product_id":9109737537741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0653\/4745\/3133\/files\/NEURO02.jpg?v=1776359714","width":1080,"height":1080},{"id":54937146654925,"created_at":"2026-04-09T09:21:39-03:00","position":3,"upda